position summary
data platform engineering's mission is to provide core development and support function for our in-house enterprise ingestion framework and peripheral product used to move and transform data in the hadoop enterprise environment our team is seeking a data platform engineer to support our growing big data ecosystem built on hadoop in this role you will collaborate with our infrastructure and data science community to develop and maintain data ingestion utility and support linux-based software product that our business customer use to derive value from data the ideal candidate ha a passion for big data technology and is excited to join u in delivering best-in-class ingestion protection and presentation capability
fundamental components
- engineer and administer big data infrastructure platform primarily based on hadoop based technology ensuring that the infrastructure is highly-available and secure
- manage security compliant user management framework for multi-tenant big data platform
- work closely with management and data scientist team to refine the big data platform to achieve company product and business objective
- collaborate with other technology team and architect to define and develop cross-function technology stack interaction
- research and experiment with emerging technology and tool related to big data
- work with the engineering management team to establish and reinforce disciplined software development process and best-practices
- maintain and support the platform on a day-to-day basis
background experience desired
- bachelor's degree in computer science or equivalent experience
- at least 2 year of experience building and managing complex product solution
- understanding of big data concept and common component including yarn queues hive beeline atscale datameer kafka and hdf
- familiarity with and use of encryption and masking technology relative to data storage and network communication
- demonstrates awareness of multiple infrastructure discipline
- 2 + year of experience with distributed highly-scalable multi-node environment
- understands the concept and technology ecosystem around both real-time and batch processing in hadoop
- familiarity in dev ops puppet chef python
- awareness of web technology and protocol java nosql json rest jms
